---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Visibility — SEO That Actually Works | Badmouth Digital" description="Get found by more people. Let the system handle what happens next. $1,500/month." currentPage="visibility">

    <!-- SECTION 1 — CONTEXT HEADER -->
    <section class="section section--hero surface-base noise-bg has-scanlines" style="position: relative; min-height: auto; padding-top: var(--space-24); padding-bottom: var(--space-12);">
        <div class="grid-page">
            <div class="col-content stack-4 text-center">
                <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-inline: auto;">
                    <span class="status-dot status-dot--live"></span>
                    <p class="t-eyebrow" style="margin: 0;">Layer 2: Visibility</p>
                </div>
                <h1 class="t-display t-display--hero" style="margin-inline: auto;">
                    GET FOUND BY<br />
                    <span style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">MORE PEOPLE.</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="t-body t-body--lg" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">
                    Let the system handle what happens next.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch;">
                    Most SEO is a waste of money. Blog posts nobody reads. Keywords nobody searches. Rankings that don't turn into calls. A monthly invoice and a report full of graphs that don't mean shit.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">
                    Our SEO sits on top of a system that's already catching and converting. Every new page, every ranking we earn, feeds directly into your lead system.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 2 — THE PROBLEM WITH SEO ALONE -->
    <section class="section section--statement section--padded surface-sunken">
        <div class="grid-page grid-align-center">
            <div class="col-left-7 stack-4">
                <p class="t-eyebrow">The Problem</p>
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section">
                    SEO WITHOUT A SYSTEM<br />
                    <span class="t-accent t-crt-shake">IS JUST EXPENSIVE BLOGGING.</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="max-width: 55ch;">
                    If your site doesn't convert, ranking #1 just means more people bounce. If follow-up doesn't trigger, leads go cold. If tracking doesn't work, you'll never know if you're throwing money into a hole.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">
                    Visibility is Layer 2. Not Layer 1. The system has to work first.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-right-5">
                <div class="retro-box" style="padding: var(--space-6);">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: var(--space-4); padding-bottom: var(--space-3); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                        <span style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal); font-size: 0.85rem;">⚠</span>
                        <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">ORDER OF OPERATIONS</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stack-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem;">
                        <p style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">✓ Foundation installed first</p>
                        <p style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">✓ System catching leads</p>
                        <p style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">✓ Follow-up firing automatically</p>
                        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-3);">→ THEN add Visibility</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3 — WHAT YOU GET -->
    <section class="section section--padded surface-base">
        <div class="grid-page grid-gap-lg">
            <div class="col-full text-center stack-4">
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="margin-inline: auto;">
                    WHAT THE VISIBILITY LAYER<br />
                    <span class="t-accent t-flicker">BUILDS OVER TIME.</span>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-full">
                <div class="inner-grid-2">
                    <div class="card stack-3" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-teal);">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">GOOGLE BUSINESS PROFILE</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Full setup, weekly posting, ongoing management. Your listing stops being a pin on a map and starts generating calls.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-teal);">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">NEW PAGES EVERY WEEK</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">One new service or area page a week. Built around what your market is searching for. Every page expands your reach.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-teal);">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">TECHNICAL SEO</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Internal linking, schema, local entity setup. The stuff that tells Google you're the real deal in your area.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card stack-3" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-teal);">
                        <h3 class="t-display t-display--card">LOCAL AUTHORITY</h3>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Citation cleanup, local link building. Consistent work that compounds over time.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PROOF -->
    <section class="section section--padded surface-elevated">
        <div class="grid-page">
            <div class="col-content stack-4">
                <p class="t-eyebrow">What This Looks Like</p>
                <div class="card" style="border-left: 3px solid var(--theme-accent-teal); padding: var(--space-6);">
                    <p class="t-body t-body--sm" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">Case Study — Garage Door Company</p>
                    <p class="t-body t-body--md">
                        Foundation installed first. Then Visibility layer activated. After 6 months: organic traffic up 340%. 22 service and area pages indexed and ranking. Google Maps visibility went from page 3 to consistent top 3. 38 additional calls per month from organic alone.
                    </p>
                    <blockquote style="margin-top: var(--space-4); padding-left: var(--space-4); border-left: 2px solid var(--color-border); font-style: italic;">
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">"We stopped paying for every lead. People just started finding us. That's when it clicked."</p>
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 4 — INVESTMENT -->
    <section class="section section--statement section--padded surface-base">
        <div class="grid-page">
            <div class="col-content stack-4 text-center">
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="margin-inline: auto;">
                    <span style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">$1,500/MONTH.</span><br />
                    <span class="t-accent t-flicker">90-DAY COMMITMENT TO START.</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch;">
                    Month-to-month after. Extra pages at $500/month.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">
                    This only kicks in after your Foundation is installed. Driving traffic to a broken system is just a faster way to waste money.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section section--cta section--padded section--mic-drop section--mic-drop--teal has-scanlines" style="position: relative;">
        <div class="grid-page" style="position: relative; z-index: 2;">
            <div class="col-content text-center stack-4">
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="color: #fff; margin-inline: auto;">
                    NEED THE FOUNDATION<br />
                    <span class="mic-drop__headline">FIRST?</span>
                </h2>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-4); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: var(--space-4);">
                    <a href="/foundation-install" class="btn btn--lg">Get Your Foundation Installed →</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--lg btn--mic-outline">Already Have One? Let's Talk</a>
                </div>
                <p style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.8rem; color: #ffffff; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-top: var(--space-3);">
                    Takes 5 minutes. We review it in 48 hours. No pitch on the first call.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>
